## Summary
This documentation page explains how to build charts in Amplitude by adding events to the Event Module, using event properties to refine analysis, and applying conditions through filtering and grouping. It details the types of events available (including default Amplitude events), how to search for events using wildcards, and how to use event properties to segment data.

